`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"more-info"}}>{`More info`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`If you need to generate a wwdr cert, you can globally install `}<MDXTag name="inlineCode" components={components} parentName="p">{`passbook`}</MDXTag>{` eg. `}<MDXTag name="inlineCode" components={components} parentName="p">{`node install -g passbook`}</MDXTag>{` and run a command like `}<MDXTag name="inlineCode" components={components} parentName="p">{`node-passbook prepare-keys -p <folder-hosting-exported-keys>`}</MDXTag>{` and it can do the conversion for you. Make sure you don't forget the password, though.`}</MDXTag>
